# formail

##### E-mail a traditional Berkeley mbox to another recipient as individual e-mails.

   formail  -Y -s /usr/sbin/sendmail bar@example.com < /var/mail/foo

##### E-mail a traditional Berkeley mbox to another recipient as individual e-mails.

   formail  -Y -s /usr/sbin/sendmail bar@example.com < /var/mail/foo
